Huntington_Park.1100 Wilshire: 1100 Wilshire is a 37-storey, 151.18 m (496.0 ft) residential skyscraper completed in 1987 in Los Angeles, California. It is the 24th tallest building in the city, the 2nd tallest residential building in the entire Southern California region, and the 4th tallest residential building in the state of California. The 35,262 m2 (379,560 sq ft) tower was designed by AC Martin Partners.
